<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 13:52:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>稳定币公司 Circle 获得令人垂涎的美国银行执照的批准</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-10/stablecoin-firm-circle-gets-approval-for-coveted-us-bank-charter</link><description>Circle Internet Group Inc. 获得批准成立一家国家数字货币信托银行来支持其稳定币业务，扩大其职权范围以涵盖机构托管服务，同时在单一联邦信托章程下巩固监管。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iaoul.OXrHUU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 11:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-10/stablecoin-firm-circle-gets-approval-for-coveted-us-bank-charter</guid></item><item><title>加密货币风险投资基金正被更令人兴奋的机会分散注意力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-07-09/crypto-vc-funds-are-getting-distracted-by-more-exciting-opportunities</link><description>加密货币风险投资基金正在转向数字资产行业之外的前景。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibrGicNqcpiE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 21:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-07-09/crypto-vc-funds-are-getting-distracted-by-more-exciting-opportunities</guid></item><item><title>比特币支持的市政债券未能获得新罕布什尔州批准</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-09/bitcoin-backed-muni-bond-fails-to-get-new-hampshire-sign-off</link><description>新罕布什尔州执行委员会投票否决了将首个比特币支持的债券推向市政市场的提议。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyFbI30VDdD4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 15:47:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-09/bitcoin-backed-muni-bond-fails-to-get-new-hampshire-sign-off</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·特朗普 (Eric Trump) 的比特币赌注让家族财富蒸发了 6 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-09/eric-trump-s-bitcoin-bet-erases-600-million-from-family-fortune</link><description>美国比特币公司是围绕一个简单的想法建立的：拥有和开采比特币就足以铸币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.UsA9BR6bIM/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 09:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-09/eric-trump-s-bitcoin-bet-erases-600-million-from-family-fortune</guid></item><item><title>特朗普言论引发新的伊朗战争担忧，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-08/bitcoin-btc-weakens-as-trump-s-remarks-raise-fresh-iran-war-concerns</link><description>随着新的地缘政治紧张局势扰乱数字资产市场，比特币暴跌，掩盖了本周早些时候对 Strategy Inc. 最新出售该代币的温和反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3NyoDhmXESA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 09:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-08/bitcoin-btc-weakens-as-trump-s-remarks-raise-fresh-iran-war-concerns</guid></item></channel></rss>